	<li><h2>Key Features: </h2></li>
	<li>Speech Recognition: Converts spoken words into text with high accuracy.</li>
	<li>Emotion Detection: Analyzes facial expressions to determine emotional states.</li>
	<li>Motion Tracking: Detects and interprets body movements for enhanced interaction.</li>
	<li>Instant Search Feature: Stores recognized text, allowing students to search for answers quickly.</li></section>
